2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the fan of r&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| Pet   | pony | goat   |
| Music-Genre   | r&b          | gospel   |
| Sport         | climbing     | lacrosse |

 